{
  "stem": "893.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Still, we secured our apartment, and we were able to get some-- some bed linen and move into our apartment, it was-- although it was too big for us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But we-- the furniture-- all the furniture was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We found some of our father's jewels hidden into-- inside the couch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They didn't think of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] looking there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably the person who-- who lived-- there was one non-Jew, who was sort of like a superintendent of the apartment building, living there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and he must have-- have raided the apartment, then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that raid must have been done after the Germans left, and between just a very short period.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We found the [? challah ?] that was probably opened up nine months ago, just before they took us-- my family away into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We found some preserved tomato that my mother cooked and preserved in bottles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We found some pictures that were thrown all over the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing of value, just-- just things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later on, we sort of managed to-- to put everything together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- what we did is, we also had a camera, a Leica.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a German, good camera that was, like, worth more than currency.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that point in time, we could use our $100-- we could get local currency.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could sell the $100 bill that we had to some other Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we also-- so we bought-- I believe that Leica I bought in Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used-- I traveled, and we used to barter, used to buy food and cigarettes and sell it to some black marketeers and-- and raise money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was another incident that happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
